     Root[0m[2m causes identified[0m[2m:
     
     **Bug[0m[2m 1: Duplicate processing[0m[2m**[0m[2m (`[0m[2mjob_queue.py:[0m[2m19[0m[2m-24[0m[2m`)
     In[0m[2m `dequeue()[0m[2m`, the `[0m[2mawait asyncio.sleep([0m[2m0.01)`[0m[2m happens AFTER finding[0m[2m a[0m[2m pending job but BEFORE[0m[2m setting status to "[0m[2mprocessing". During[0m[2m that[0m[2m await, other workers[0m[2m can find[0m[2m the same job[0m[2m still marked[0m[2m "pending" and[0m[2m grab[0m[2m it.[0m[2m
     
